quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  8,41,WE A’LEMU ‘ENNEMA GANIMTUM MIN SHEJ’IN FE’ENNE LILLAHI HUMUSEHU WE LILRRESULI WE LIDHIL-KURBA WEL-JETAMA WEL-MESAKINI WE EBNI ES-SEBILI ‘IN KUNTUM ‘AMENTUM BILLAHI WE MA ‘ENZELNA ‘ALA ‘ABDINA JEWMEL-FURKANI JEWMET-TEKAL-XHEM’ANI WEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’I
  8,42,‘IDH ‘ENTUM BIL-’UDWETI ED-DUNJA WE HUM BIL-’UDWETIL-KUSWA WE ER-REKBU ‘ESFELE MINKUM WE LEW TEWA’ADTTUM LAHTELEFTUM FIL-MI’ADI WE LEKIN LIJEKDIJEL-LAHU ‘EMRÆN KANE MEF’ULÆN LIJEHLIKE MEN HELEKE ‘AN BEJJINETIN WE JEHJA MEN HEJJE ‘AN BEJJINETIN WE ‘INNALL
  8,43,‘IDH JURIKEHUMU ELLAHU FI MENAMIKE KALILÆN WE LEW ‘ERAKEHUM KETHIRÆN LEFESHILTUM WE LETENAZA’TUM FIL-’EMRI WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE SELLEME ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  8,44,WE ‘IDH JURIKUMUHUM ‘IDHIT-TEKAJTUM FI ‘A’JUNIKUM KALILÆN WE JUKALLILUKUM FI ‘A’JUNIHIM LIJEKDIJEL-LAHU ‘EMRÆN KANE MEF’ULÆN WE ‘ILA ELLAHI TURXHA’UL-’UMURU
  8,45,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA LEKITUM FI’ETEN FATHBUTU WE EDHKURU ELLAHE KETHIRÆN LE’ALLEKUM TUFLIHUNE
  8,46,WE ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE RESULEHU WE LA TENAZA’U FETEFSHELU WE TEDH/HEBE RIHUKUM WE ESBIRU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ME’A ES-SABIRINE
  8,47,WE LA TEKUNU KALLEDHINE HAREXHU MIN DIJARIHIM BETERÆN WE RI’A’E EN-NASI WE JESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WEL-LAHU BIMA JA’MELUNE MUHITUN
  8,48,WE ‘IDH ZEJJENE LEHUMU ESH-SHEJTANU ‘A’MALEHUM WE KALE LA GALIBE LEKUMUL-JEWME MINE EN-NASI WE ‘INNI XHARUN LEKUM FELEMMA TERA’ETIL-FI’ETANI NEKESE ‘ALA ‘AKIBEJHI WE KALE ‘INNI BERI’UN MINKUM ‘INNI ‘ERA MA LA TEREWNE ‘INNIJI ‘EHAFU ELLAHE WEL-LAHU SHEDIDU
  8,49,‘IDH JEKULUL-MUNAFIKUNE WEL-LEDHINE FI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN GARRE HA’UULA’ DINUHUM WE MEN JETEWEKKEL ‘ALA ELLAHI FE’INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN HEKIMUN
  8,50,WE LEW TERA ‘IDH JETEWEFFAL-LEDHINE KEFERUL-MELA’IKETU JEDRIBUNE WUXHUHEHUM WE ‘EDBAREHUM WE DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HERIKI
  8,51,DHALIKE BIMA KADDEMET ‘EJDIKUM WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LEJSE BIDHELLAMIN LIL’ABIDI
  8,52,KEDE’BI ‘ALI FIR’AWNE WEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM KEFERU BI’AJATI ELLAHI FE’EHADHEHUMU ELLAHU BIDHUNUBIHIM ‘INNALL-LLAHE KAWIJUN SHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  8,53,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE LEM JEKU MUGAJJIRÆN NI’METEN ‘EN’AMEHA ‘ALA KAWMIN HETTA JUGAJJIRU MA BI’ENFUSIHIM WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE SEMI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  8,54,KEDE’BI ‘ALI FIR’AWNE WEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM FE’EHLEKNAHUM BIDHUNUBIHIM WE ‘EGREKNA ‘ALE FIR’AWNE WE KULLUN KANU DHALIMINE
  8,55,‘INNE SHERRE ED-DEWABBI ‘INDEL-LAHIL-LEDHINE KEFERU FEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  8,56,EL-LEDHINE ‘AHEDTE MINHUM THUMME JENKUDUNE ‘AHDEHUM FI KULLI MERRETIN WE HUM LA JETTEKUNE
  8,57,FE’IMMA TETHKAFENNEHUM FIL-HERBI FESHERRID BIHIM MEN HALFEHUM LE’ALLEHUM JEDHDHEKKERUNE
  8,58,WE ‘IMMA TEHAFENNE MIN KAWMIN HIJANETEN FANBIDH ‘ILEJHIM ‘ALA SEWA’IN ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUHIBBUL-HA’ININE
  8,59,WE LA JEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU SEBEKU ‘INNEHUM LA JU’XHIZUNE
  8,60,WE ‘A’IDDU LEHUM MA ESTETA’TUM MIN KUWETIN WE MIN RIBATIL-HAJLI TURHIBUNE BIHI ‘ADUWEL-LAHI WE ‘ADUWEKUM WE ‘AHARINE MIN DUNIHIM LA TA’LEMUNEHUMU ELLAHU JA’LEMUHUM WE MA TUNFIKU MIN SHEJ’IN FI SEBILI ELLAHI JUWEFFE ‘ILEJKUM WE ‘ENTUM LA TUDHLEMUNE